p.d: Following a successful first run, The Outdoor Sports Show has returned on screens in early 2018, by showcasing a diverse array of outdoor sports destined to reach again millions of audiences globally. There are no limits to the content of the Outdoor Sports Show, which covers everything, from professional and recreational to the extreme and adventure sports. From marathon races to climbing, skiing to surfing, hiking to triathlon, sailing to cycling - human meets nature on a thrilling journey of performance.
